item.title: CVE-2019-10791|2024-08-04T22:32:02.100Z -- snyk -- promise-probe
item.description: promise-probe before 0.10.0 allows remote attackers to perform a command injection attack. The file, outputFile and options functions can be controlled by users without any sanitization.
